data.description: This 4 bed 3 bath home is located on state maintained hwy with a private country setting! Not far from town and in a good school district. This house has plenty of parking, attached 2 car garage and a large walkout basement. All livable on one level, this home would be perfect for anyone wanting elbow room, regardless of their age. Many updates throughout and a semi open floorplan allows you to truly enjoy the time you spend at home.
